{"pageProps":{"eyebrow":"工具链","page":{"layout":"document","title":"exporter","description":"An prometheus and OpenTelemetry exporter for custom eBPF metrics, written in async rust: eunomia-exporter","bodyHtml":"<p>An prometheus and OpenTelemetry exporter for custom eBPF metrics, written in async rust: eunomia-exporter</p>\n<p>This is a single binary exporter, you don't need to install <code>BCC/LLVM</code> when you use it. The only thing you will need to run the exporter on another machine is the config file and pre-compiled eBPF code.</p>\n<h2 id=\"supported-scenarios\">Supported scenarios</h2>\n<p>Currently the only supported way of getting data out of the kernel is via maps (we call them tables in configuration).</p>","headings":[{"id":"supported-scenarios","text":"Supported scenarios","depth":2}],"sourcePath":"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia.dev/tree/main/docs/eunomia-bpf/exporter/index.md","metadata":{"updatedAt":"2024-01-26T22:09:57.000Z","createdAt":"2023-08-10T12:54:12.000Z","authors":[{"name":"云微","email":"1067852565@qq.com"},{"name":"oluceps","email":"ospp@oluceps.uk"}]},"path":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/exporter/","alternates":{"en":"/eunomia-bpf/exporter/","zh":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/exporter/"},"continuation":{"index":{"title":"eunomia-bpf：简化并增强eBPF，支持CO-RE[^1]和WebAssembly[^2]","description":"![GitHub release (latest by date)](https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf/releases) ![codecov](https://codecov.io/gh/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf) ![DeepSource](https://deepsource.io/gh/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf/?ref=reposi","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/"},"previous":{"title":"ecli server","description":"ecli-server 和 ecli client 子命令已在 2026 年 3 月从主分支移除，以降低维护复杂度。","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecli/server/"},"next":{"title":"usage","description":"This is an adapted version of opensnoop from bcc/libbpf-tools, you can check our source code here: examples/bpftools/opensnoop","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/exporter/usage/"}},"sidebar":[{"title":"eunomia-bpf：简化并增强eBPF，支持CO-RE[^1]和WebAssembly[^2]","it